@startuml
title Oracle Offset - Componentes da Implementacao

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor Usuario

component "Cliente\nusuario.py" as Cliente
component "Oraculo API\noraculo.py" as Oraculo
component "Sender\nblockchain_sender.py" as Sender
database "Contrato\nCarbonCreditNFT_E1.sol" as Contrato

Usuario --> Cliente : Interacao local
Cliente --> Oraculo : /processar_trajeto\n/confirmar_opcao
Oraculo --> Sender : send_oracle_results(...)
Cliente --> Sender : send_oracle_results(...)
Sender --> Contrato : chamadas de metodos
Cliente --> Contrato : leitura (hash/token)

note right of Contrato
  Metodos principais:
  - calculateAndMintWithHash
  - mintWithOracleValue
  - isTrajectoryHashRegistered
  - requestRedeemByHash
end note

@enduml
